h to talk\nwith another one using Wi-Fi over a heterogeneous connection where the\nend-to-end jitter is mainly below 20ms and the packet loss rate is as small as\n0.2 per cent.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Jan 2017 12:10:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-10"}
